# Security Rules

Compiled from C2DS-brood, C2DS-bootstrap, GGG-*, ELSL-* AGENTS.md.

## Credentials and Secrets

- **NEVER** hardcode credentials, passwords, API keys, or tokens
- **NEVER** log sensitive data (passwords, private keys, certs) in any build
- Keep certificates in `.gitignore`d directories

## Input Validation

- Validate all external inputs (NULL checks, bounds checks)
- Validate all buffer operations for overflow
- Reject invalid device IDs, malformed JSON, etc.
